headline: ADM Declares Cash Dividend
summary: CHICAGO, August 06, 2025--ADM’s (NYSE: ADM) Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of 51.0 cents per share on the company’s common stock. The dividend is payable on Sept. 10, 2025, to shareholders of record on Aug. 20, 2025.
